description: The investment seeks capital appreciation. Under normal conditions, the fund invests in equity securities of companies of any capitalization that are traded on U.S. exchanges and exchange traded funds ("ETFs") that primarily invest in U.S. equity securities ("Equity ETFs"). The adviser's models may also direct for investment in ETFs that invest in treasury bonds, volatility ETFs and exchange-traded notes ("ETNs") and leveraged and inverse ETFs.
name: Trend Aggregation U.S. ETF
